Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙到底什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Luminous Heartiel Action
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whip Decoration
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那是光之美少女的技能吧
