Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
