Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊 Cure Yell 我是花啊
